<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听见有人在哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用X射线透过房子往里看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>穿过一条长长的走廊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在一个黑暗的房间，罗西看到了两个人影。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个穿得像僧人的男人正在哭，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个看起来像个紫色的怪物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们被绳子绑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟净，现在要怎么办！” 僧人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能去西天取经了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，师父。” 悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看马的时候，被妖怪抓住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们人太多，我打不过他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>僧人哭得更厉害了：“我们马上就要被……吃掉了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！” 罗西惊讶地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地主抓了他们——还有人要吃了他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地主走回房间：“没错！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，漂亮的房间变成了黑暗的山洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地主长着尖牙和长角，非常丑陋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是妖怪！” 罗西大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成汽车，去追厄尔和德怀特。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开得很快，在拐角处打滑了，差点儿撞上另一辆汽车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机向悟空挥了挥拳头：“看看路，你这个疯狂的司机！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！” 悟空大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强盗们把车开出城，又开了很长一段路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他们在一个大楼旁边停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变回自己，躲了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强盗们从车上下来，仔细看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总算摆脱了那只可怕的猴子。” 德怀特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只猴子才没吓到我。” 厄尔哼了一声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？” 德怀特摇了摇头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也跟我一样尖叫着跑出来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得那只猴子非常可怕！” 一个声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德怀特看了看四周：“谁在说话？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只松鼠沿着栏杆走过来：“是我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听见了吗，德怀特？” 厄尔说，“会说话的松鼠！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先是会说话的猴子。” 德怀特说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又是会说话的松鼠……到底发生了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>松鼠坐下来，突然又变成了猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那只猴子！” 德怀特和厄尔大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，是我。” 悟空笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们两个笨蛋被逮捕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们想要逃跑，但悟空跳到了他们面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抓住他们的胳膊大喊：“你们跟我走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抓着两个强盗跳到一朵云上。咻！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，德怀特，我们在飞！” 厄尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德怀特闭上眼睛，没有回答他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到美罗城后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空来到真实储蓄银行，找到了史密斯侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，侦探！” 悟空笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抓住了强盗，没有伤害他们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做得好，悟空！” 史密斯侦探高兴地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探和悟空把两个强盗送进了美罗城监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看四周：“这个监狱里有很多坏人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探耸了耸肩：“不是很多。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空听到有人在打呼噜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个声音……” 悟空仔细地听了听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼噜噜，呼噜噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个呼噜声怎么这么熟悉！” 悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑向一间牢房，一头大猪正在里面睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑起来：“找到八戒了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>